{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_07_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 3話 いいとこ取りしちゃおう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――新MV撮影日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of shooting new MV",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか{user}さん、この新しい衣装\nすっっっごくいいと思いませんか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do you like the new outfits‚ {user}-san?\nAren't they just absolutely amazing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、凄くいいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ they're really great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0355098406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9888432263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。愛ちゃんと二人でデザイナーさんと\n議論を重ねて辿り着いた、究極のデザインですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they are. Ai-chan and I worked\nclosely with the designer to perfect them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.049183313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……なのに、先輩達の反応がうっす～いから\n褒めてくれる人を探してたんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But our seniors' reactions were so lukewarm‚\nso I was looking for someone to praise us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　莉央さんと葵も喜んでいたけど\n二人に任せて良かったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Rio-san and Aoi were happy about it‚\nthey said they were glad they left it to you two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8764618238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.6001365105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あの～、{user}さん\n優しい嘘は時に人を傷つけるものなんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san‚\nsometimes kind lies can hurt people‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "だって莉央さんは「合格よ」としか言わないし\n葵さんは「いいんじゃない？」ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Rio-san only said‚ \"It's acceptable‚\"\nand Aoi-san said‚ \"It's fine.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5062585274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こころはすぐ調子に乗るから\nあえて直接言わなかったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe they didn't say more because they know\nKokoro tend to get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7359172822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな～。頑張ったこころと愛ちゃんを……\n特にこころを素直に褒めてくれたらいいのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ come on. After all our hard work‚\nespecially Kokoro‚ they could've just praised us honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.3386770327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも葵も素直じゃないからな\nでも、そんな二人に憧れていたんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi aren't very straightforward‚\nbut you've always admired them‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5016693117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そうなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's true. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.644187808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3436884005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、{user}さん\nこころは今回の件で愛ちゃんに気付かされました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ {user}-san‚\nI realized something thanks to Ai-chan during this project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1666683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.414232548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、先輩達に憧れる気持ちから\n目をそらそうとしてたんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was trying to avoid my feelings of admiration\nfor our seniors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5666683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそう思ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you think that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3936039368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7689810354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、先輩達二人の『GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world』を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt like I had to surpass the seniors'\nperformance of \"GIRI-GIRI borderless world\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4666779835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "何がなんでも超えなくちゃいけないと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.512875835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3450980424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "そのためには、先輩達と同じことをしてちゃダメで\n衣装を、いろんなことを、変えなくちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That meant we couldn't do the same thing as them‚\nand we had to change the outfits and everything else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.433339564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "……そのことばかりを考えて\n大切なことが目に入らなくなっちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was so focused on that\nthat I lost sight of what's really important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.7909193913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "だから先輩達の衣装と違うデザインにこだわって\n愛ちゃんに対しても意固地になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I insisted on a different design from the seniors' outfits…\nand I became stubborn with Ai-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "もし、あのまま突っ走っていたら\n昔からのファンをがっかりさせていたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we had kept going like that‚\nwe would've disappointed our long-time fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.7915319045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。莉央さんと葵なら\nきっとそんなことはしないはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. Rio-san and Aoi\nwould never let that happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9603071694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい。そんなんじゃ先輩達の『GIRI-GIRI』を\n超えることなんて、出来っこないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. There's no way we can surpass the seniors' \"GIRI-GIRI\"\nwith something like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.8286984682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "だから、今と昔のいいとこ取りしちゃおう\nって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought‚ let's take the best parts of\nboth the past and the present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7684490283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、今回の新衣装は今のトレンドを取り入れつつ\n以前のデザインの雰囲気もしっかり残っていると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ this new outfit blends the current trends while\nretaining the vibe of the previous design.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3643673425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0871109407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。無理に変えなくていい\nいいものはそのままでいいんだって気付いたら",
      "translations": {
